handleResponse(HttpResponse, Delivery) - Method in class com.duowan.mobile.netroid.request.FileDownloadRequest
In this method, we got the Content-Length, with the TemporaryFile length, we can calculate the actually size of the whole file, if TemporaryFile not exists, we'll take the store file length then compare to actually size, and if equals, we consider this download was already done.
handleResponse(HttpResponse, Delivery) - Method in class com.duowan.mobile.netroid.Request
Handle the response for various request, normally, a request was a short and low memory-usage request, thus we can parse the response-content as byte[] in memory.
